6) Counters took a break from 2:30 to 3:00 PM. Data for this
7) Counter Notes: Several “close calls” occurred throughout the day. Vehicles attempting to turn left off of
Old Poole Road onto Poole Road often used the two-way-left-turn lane as a refuge lane. Also, multiple
vehicles turning left onto Poole Road went around less aggressive vehicles waiting for a gap to make the
same movement. At approximately 4:00 PM, the intersection just to the west of the counted intersection,
at Poole Road & I-440 Ramps, lost power to its signals for about 1 hour due to storms in the area. No
increased delays at the subject intersection were noted due to this temporary power outage.
